"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-02-paris-2024-olympics-enekwechi-advances-to-mens-shot-put-final\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Nigeria's Chukwuebuka Enekwechi has made it to the final of the men's shot put event at the 2024 Olympic Games, DAILY POST reports.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9884915464324694, \"rank\": 0.011219221956662641, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chukwuebuka_Enekwechi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chukwuebuka Enekwechi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chukwuebuka_Enekwechi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chukwuebuka_Enekwechi\"}, {\"begin\": 131, \"end\": 141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"score\": 0.9999999999994316, \"rank\": 5.393402756525735e-13, \"text\": \"DAILY POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enekwechi advanced into Saturday's final, placing fifth overall in qualification Group B.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old threw a distance of 21.13m to earn himself a place in the final.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The African champion is the first Nigerian to make it to the final of any event at the ongoing games.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 359, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.9987596748481055, \"rank\": 0.001225788026433467, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be recalled that Enekwechi made it to the final of the shot put event four years ago in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9983637207216306, \"rank\": 0.001275594967102275, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would be hoping to make it to the podium by finishing in the top three.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three NPFL clubs jostle for Ernest's signature  Edo Queens sign 14 new players for CAF Women's Champions League qualifier  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's dismal performance worries enthusiasts  Paris 2024 Olympics: D'Tigress' Wakama wins Best Coach award  Paris 2024 Olympics: Brume vows to  bounce back from disappointing outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Sports Minister apologises to Nigerians after disastrous outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Team Nigeria officially finishes without single medal  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's last medal hope Reuben crashes out in Wrestling  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Professional_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999938609, \"rank\": 6.136556391792462e-12, \"text\": \"NPFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Professional_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Professional_Football_League\"}, {\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ernest_Hemingway\", \"score\": 0.97440101723087, \"rank\": 0.0262715066135429